
The module user includes a class of 'User' who has a user name and a list of people he follows, the user can add people to his
following list, as well as posting a new post with a given message. The module also includes a global list of posts
which includes all the posts from the list of users in the platform.

The module social_media allows registration of new users to the platform if they are not already registered, as well as
generating the timeline for each user, which is all the posts from people the user follows.
